<template>
    <basic-block 
        class="cuttingblock"
        :block-width="blockWidth"
        :block-height="blockHeight"
        :side-color="'rgb(171,146,26)'"> 
  <slot></slot>
  </basic-block>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    props:{
        blockWidth:{
            type: String,
            required: false,
            default: '30%'
        },
        blockHeight:{
            type: String,
            required: false,
            default: '80%'
        }
    }
}
</script>

</style>
